thread.title: Sarah Convery

author: Sarah Convery
title: Sarah Convery
text: We have leased Servcorp offices in Australia and Overseas for a number of years. We have always received excellent service and a clear description of service offerings. They have the ease of booking online for any location, friendly staff that go out of their way to assist, and they consistently meet the expectations of a serviced office or virtual office anywhere in the world. Servcorp is a place where you can bring your clients to do business and be completely satisfied with your choice of meeting place.
